卫生：房间宽敞舒适，卫生整洁。
环境：花园环境美丽，大堂华丽。
服务：各处服务人员热情周到，待客如宾。', '2024-01-15', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''房间设施'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232y12000cxy8v335F24_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235m12000cxy94s34C3D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234912000cxy91qsEC04_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '超值的享受！', '超值的享受！
住酒店这么多年，我认为花园酒店是我迄今为止住过最好的酒店。
现在太难找到一家这么有文化底蕴的酒店了。
如果外地游客来广州玩，强烈建议就住这里，可以浓缩地快速地了解广府文化。', '2023-11-06', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''性价比'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231212000ciwb8eb18EC_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231812000ciwiy28F092_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230212000ciw7qch2D4C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231s12000ciwbpcnE3C8_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232w12000ciweutf592D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232n12000ciwbnoa775E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230w12000ciwd31f0C84_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232n12000ciwbsi39B9C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234312000ciwfjmxF444_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '来广州探亲，这次定的花园酒店，大堂还是那么华丽，房间干净，那么多年保持得非常好?', '来广州探亲，这次定的花园酒店，大堂还是那么华丽，房间干净，那么多年保持得非常好??附近喝茶也非常方便，下次还会来！', '2024-01-14', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''卫生状况'', ''周边配套'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233y12000cxnxzwc22C4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234u12000cxny2xf1597_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231z12000cxnxx9a8000_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间布草很舒服。服务很好??', '房间布草很舒服。服务很好??', '2024-04-10', 5, '[''房间设施'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236312000dn363lg6A50_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232612000dn374urB22B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232f12000dn35g36E451_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '预售套餐特别划算，1050的红棉大床房大概有100平，两个卫生间，住起来很舒服，', '预售套餐特别划算，1050的红棉大床房大概有100平，两个卫生间，住起来很舒服，赠送的500无门槛餐券也性价比极高。

