50_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '广州的老字号酒店，名不虚传，值得专门打卡，无论是吃饭还是住宿', '广州的老字号酒店，名不虚传，值得专门打卡，无论是吃饭还是住宿

位于市中心，楼下有地铁，出行便利。

房间翻新过，硬件设施很好，房间很大。特别喜欢那个大书桌，加班??绝配除了洗护用品不够高档，木有戴森，堪称完美

行政酒廊环境很好，食物简单，但是对付一口绰绰有余

酒店入住率相当高，但是服务，品质不打折。房间有酒店和周边介绍，感觉酒店就可以玩一整天

旁边在修地铁，白天是真的吵，晚上安静的', '2023-10-21', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''交通便利性'', ''房间设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230e12000cfio9kh09E1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232112000cfinwh1B25E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230512000cfio2bd165C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231t12000cfipg0lC745_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230512000cfiqjfkE103_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234212000cfis4rj5C05_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232512000cfisan54178_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234r12000cfinm22B339_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '十分满意，无论是酒店环境还是服务，以后来广州还会继续选择花园酒店作为入住酒店，携', '十分满意，无论是酒店环境还是服务，以后来广州还会继续选择花园酒店作为入住酒店，携程预订也很方便快捷。赞赞赞', '2024-01-01', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230j224x8toahcrz92CE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230l224x8toaizpp58A1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235d224x8toa8bp9AD74_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/02352224x8toaesiy94D9_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/02358224x8toahcs7F386_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '广州首选酒店！', '广州首选酒店！', '2024-06-05', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231w12000ec2mye05BF5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236z12000ec2yywg091C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230x12000ec3831yA31A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]');